{"tid":2456562,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田61歲阿婆玩交友app識「美國軍醫」　被騙6萬元","createTime":"2021-03-22T04:50:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T10:47:15.000Z","uid":44209,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fd9639fc640dcdbde53a913e388e8b6e765a9dd1","tid":2456562,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T04:50:36.000Z","msg":"2021-03-21 23:21<br />\n<br />\n網上交友易墮騙局，沙田一名婦人失財6萬元。今（21日）下午2時許，警方接獲沙田水泉澳邨一名姓張61歲婦人報案，指早前使用通訊程式時結識一名自稱為美國軍醫的男子，雙方相談甚歡，女事主亦放下戒心，其間更按對方指示將約5.1萬元人民幣（即約6.1萬港元）存入一個銀行戶口，以收取一個包裹。女事主其後懷疑自己被騙，遂報警求助。警方接報到場，經初步調查，案件列以欺騙手段取得財產，交由沙田警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。"},{"pid":"ef8a15b9062c296f1980bf90dca32c9ba1c5e143","tid":2456562,"uid":208713,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T04:55:03.000Z","msg":"阿婆都要大巨腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea21cf45175ca99a81a95716bf0100ec5a1e2c3","tid":2456562,"uid":325556,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T04:57:07.000Z","msg":"美國軍醫要人民幣 中國強大了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2aa89ad679506445d7ca2bbb18ee546b2152bb7","tid":2456562,"uid":387307,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:00:08.000Z","msg":"睇標題笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e817ef112cf844b05e0ec632049b3363020cad","tid":2456562,"uid":146243,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:00:15.000Z","msg":"阿婆勾結外國軍方勢力 <br />\n仲提供埋資金<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ab0010fb10fafa6e072e329d939dc18b0209d2","tid":2456562,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:04:38.000Z","msg":"61戱阿婆交友app十個九個都只係黃世澤呢類既戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\